creator: Integer5
descriptionHtml:
Live Schedule fort he upcomming Football European Championship 2021
⚽ With the Euro 2021 schedule you can follow the play process of every game. The livescores and the liveticker are clearly presented. This event refers to the postponed Euro 2020. This app presents all Matches over the whole tournament and a table of all participating groups.

Liveticker
📢 Receive all important events of all Euro 2021 games in the liveticker, to be update on the happenings. This includes: elapsed time, the livescores, goals and their scorer, yellow cards, red cards and substitutions. Currently there are no notifications for goals and events possible.

Simple handling of the application
📲 The clear structured design of the app allows an intuitive usage of the app. By tapping on any match on the Euro 2021 schedule, the liveticker is presented below the live results.
This Euro 2021 Schedule app is free and concentrated on the most important information to follow the progress oft the European Championship.
